  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Carbon Dioxide Insufflation During Endoscopy</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Assessment of Differences in Clinical Safety and Efficacy of Carbon Dioxide Insufflation During Sedated and Conventional Endoscopy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
